{
  "stem": "19921.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 97.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In all those camps, I want you to know, all those camps which we liberated, now Sobibor, where we didn't stay longer than 45 minutes. 45 minutes.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Majdanek, we stayed close to two hours.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, to look around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To look around.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We saw, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All the, all the barracks were left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All the barracks were left.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They-- I know they were all painted neatly green.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The area was nice and clean, kept very nice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The barbed wire and they had all those watch towers which they have, everything was erect, and nothing was taken down.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The only thing which was destroyed, later we found out and we were also told by the political people there, that it was their building from their, from their commander of that camp, a German commander.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know his name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't remember the name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But a, a German commander was living in that, that building was partially destroyed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's the only-- it was a wooden building, like one-family house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was right next to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Didn't bother him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was right there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there were also gardens which we saw.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There were gardens there, which they, they planted, the SS people which were living there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Nearby, they had big gardens.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There, later, we found out the ash was used for the gardens too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very badly.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Do you know, you know, this is the first time-- I'm not a crier.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was sent away, you know, from my parents, and I was still a kid, really, 16 years old.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in, in, in Poland, you were a kid.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Today, you're a 16-year-old, you're a little bit more mature.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they were, you know, you were sheltered by your mother, by your grandfather, by everybody.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So you were still a kid.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
